---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section
    class="hero-gradient pt-32 pb-12 px-6 lg:px-12 overflow-hidden relative"
>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6 relative z-10">
            <div
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 bg-white/60 border border-[var(--line)] rounded-full backdrop-blur-md"
            >
                <span
                    class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-[var(--verde)] rounded-full animate-pulse"
                ></span>
                <span
                    class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-extrabold text-[var(--ink)]"
                    >La herramienta que usa la FP del País Vasco</span
                >
            </div>
            <h1
                class="serif text-7xl lg:text-8xl leading-[0.95] text-[var(--ink)] tracking-tight"
            >
                El software para gestionar <em>todo el DUAL.</em>
            </h1>
            <!-- 
            <p
                class="text-gray-500 text-lg lg:text-xl max-w-xl leading-relaxed"
            >
                Una plataforma integral que conecta centros, empresas y alumnos
                para maximizar el potencial de la formación profesional.
            </p>
            -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-5">
                <a
                    class="bg-[var(--rosa)] text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-full font-bold shadow-2xl shadow-pink-500/25 hover:scale-105 transition-transform"
                    href="#cta">Empezar ahora</a
                >
                <a
                    class="bg-white px-10 py-5 rounded-full font-bold border border-[var(--line)] hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors flex items-center gap-2"
                    href="#func"
                    >Explorar sistema <span
                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm"
                        >arrow_forward</span
                    >
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--verde-soft)]/60 to-[var(--rosa-soft)]/60 p-6 rounded-2xl">
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                    "Mediante la colaboración de los centros de FP referentes del País Vasco, hemos desarrollado una plataforma que gestiona el DUAL de principio a fin: búsqueda y captación de empresas; selección automática del alumnado; generación de la documentación, firma y custodia; creación automática de calendarios, seguimiento en tiempo real y evaluación por competencias. Menos carga administrativa, más control, seguridad, eficiencia y una visión completa del proceso en un único entorno."
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
                    <img
                        src="/images/zigor-esnaola.jpg"
                        alt="Zigor Esnaola"
                        class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover flex-shrink-0"
                    />
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
                            Zigor Esnaola
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                            Responsable de formación · Vocal coordinador de la asociación FPEmpresa<br/>
                            <span class="font-semibold">IMH · Centro de FP, País Vasco</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
            <div
                class="relative z-20 bg-white p-2 rounded-[32px] shadow-[0_32px_80px_-20px_rgba(26,10,36,0.15)] premium-border"
            >
                <div class="bg-[#F9FAFB] rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden">
                    <div
                        class="px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-100 bg-white"
                    >
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400/20">
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-amber-400/20">
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-400/20">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-50 rounded-md text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400"
                        >
                            DASHBOARD DUAL365
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
                            <div
                                class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm premium-border"
                            >
                                <p
                                    class="text-gray-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1"
                                >
                                    Empresas Activas
                                </p>
                                <div class="flex items-end gap-2">
                                    <span
                                        class="serif text-4xl text-[var(--ink)]"
                                        >842</span
                                    >
                                    <span
                                        class="text-[var(--verde)] text-xs font-bold mb-1"
                                        >+12%</span
                                    >
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm premium-border"
                            >
                                <p
                                    class="text-gray-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1"
                                >
                                    SATISFACCIÓN
                                </p>
                                <div class="flex items-end gap-2">
                                    <span
                                        class="serif text-4xl text-[var(--rosa)]"
                                        >94%</span
                                    >
                                    <span
                                        class="text-[var(--rosa)] text-xs font-bold mb-1"
                                        >Optimo</span
                                    >
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm premium-border"
                        >
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sm">
                                    Distribución por Especialidad
                                </h4>
                                <span
                                    class="material-symbols-outlined text-gray-400 text-sm"
                                    >more_horiz</span
                                >
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="flex items-end gap-3 h-32 justify-between px-2"
                            >
                                <div
                                    class="w-full bg-[var(--rosa-soft)] rounded-t-lg relative group"
                                    style="height: 60%"
                                >
                                    <div
                                        class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[9px] font-bold hidden group-hover:block"
                                    >
                                        60%
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="w-full bg-[var(--verde-soft)] rounded-t-lg relative group"
                                    style="height: 85%"
                                >
                                    <div
                                        class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[9px] font-bold hidden group-hover:block"
                                    >
                                        85%
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="w-full bg-indigo-50 rounded-t-lg relative group"
                                    style="height: 45%"
                                >
                                    <div
                                        class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[9px] font-bold hidden group-hover:block"
                                    >
                                        45%
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="w-full bg-amber-50 rounded-t-lg relative group"
                                    style="height: 70%"
                                >
                                    <div
                                        class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[9px] font-bold hidden group-hover:block"
                                    >
                                        70%
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="w-full bg-[var(--rosa-mid)] rounded-t-lg relative group"
                                    style="height: 95%"
                                >
                                    <div
                                        class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[9px] font-bold hidden group-hover:block"
                                    >
                                        95%
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-64 h-64 bg-[var(--rosa)]/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] -z-10"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute -bottom-12 -left-12 w-80 h-80 bg-[var(--verde)]/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] -z-10"
            >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .hero-gradient {
        background: radial-gradient(
                circle at 10% 20%,
                var(--rosa-pale) 0%,
                transparent 60%
            ),
            radial-gradient(
                circle at 90% 80%,
                var(--verde-pale) 0%,
                transparent 60%
            ),
            radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #ffffff 0%, #fcfcfc 100%);
    }
</style>
